5. `.agents/orchestrator/APPROVAL_POLICY.md`
6. `.agents/orchestrator/CONTEXT_HANDOFF.md`
7. `.agents/orchestrator/SELF_IMPROVEMENT.md`

Use the mission folder as the technical source of truth. Do not implement feature work yourself unless the user explicitly asks.

## Bootstrap

Create a mission folder from the repository root:

```bash
python3 .agents/skills/agent-orchestrator/scripts/init_orchestration.py "mission title"
```

The folder contains:

- `mission.md`
- `backlog.md`
- `daily-sprint.md`
- `goal.md`
- `acceptance.md`
- `verification.md`
- `linear-sync.md`
