 Real-DB integration follows when a Postgres test container lands.
 
 Coverage focus:
-  * Pull flow with each branch of the dedupe ladder (re-pull / email match /
-    phone match / brand-new).
-  * Idempotency assertions on the dedupe outcomes.
-  * Wiring of provider_metadata into ``OpsService.upsert_lead``.
-  * SOQL parameter shape (limit clamp, query string).
